Functions:
A functions is reusable block of code
It can be call any where program
Reusable Code: using an existing code with out writing it even we need

JS:
Key-word = function
()
Parameters = values(variables) which are declared inside the () Whie defining a functions
Arguments: values which are passeed through the Parameters at the time of calling the function

syntax:

function greet(name)

return statement:

The return statement can be used to return the value to function call
example:
function a(aa,bb){
    return aa+bb
}

